  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model is intended to predict absolute hemolysis index for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5 operating at 3500 RPM and 5 L/min flow. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification spans viscosity, inlet velocity, and RBC fragility parameters. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated; seven factors achieved required levels and six were assessed with marginal gaps that were resolved through supplementary bench validation. Decision: Accepted for the intended regulatory submission supporting 510(k) substantial equivalence argument.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/cou2-vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cou2-cfd-hemolysis-absolute-prediction",
